{"id":249109,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-北京维权律师李长青在常州被绑架殴打（/","date":"2012-08-28T05:01:22Z","modified":"2012-08-28T05:01:22Z","title":"维权网 | 北京维权律师李长青在常州被绑架殴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，北京汉卓律师事务所维权律师李长青在江苏常州市湖塘镇东升村谈忠义家与湖塘镇政府谈判过程中，有多位拆迁公司人员把李长青律师从谈忠义家强行带走，塞入一辆红色的轿车，左右各一人，副驾驶一人把李长青律师挟持到东升村委会，然后遭到身份不明人员侮辱、谩骂和殴打。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，李长青律师在被绑架到东升村委后，手机被自称拆迁公司法定代表人的周亚平（音）摔烂，电池和手机屏被用力拧坏，已经彻底报废。李长青律师额头、腿、膝盖等多处受伤，直到警察把李长青律师接到派出所，才得以脱身。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>早</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点，马杭镇强拆了村民白明治的家，当时白明治还在睡梦中，被人破开大门后把他蒙头带到十几里外扔下，回来后发现房屋被铲平。随后村民谈忠义家遭到威胁，并在电话中威胁律师。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，马杭镇镇长与李长青律师通电话，要求李长青律师去见他，李律师在与镇长的会见中，遭到绑架殴打。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VH_o1DaQfVw/UDw5NcNm1II/AAAAAAAAMSM/0bE_zBKgj-Q/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VH_o1DaQfVw/UDw5NcNm1II/AAAAAAAAMSM/0bE_zBKgj-Q/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" width=\"291\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VDXXEQ4RXC8/UDw5Q6j92DI/AAAAAAAAMSU/waUFgEV5WVY/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VDXXEQ4RXC8/UDw5Q6j92DI/AAAAAAAAMSU/waUFgEV5WVY/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"309\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7600901074246283992?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}